Despite how much time we spend on them, the numbers on a do anything to get back.
character sheet aren’t everything. Much of the fun of role-playing
is creating a character who feels like a believable part of their Who Are You Loyal To?
world, but it can often be difficult to decide where to start. You Real loners are rare: Tamriel can be a dangerous place without
